data.description: OPEN THIS SUNDAY NOVEMBER 26TH FROM 12-3 PM. Beautiful, brick, freshly painted Townhome with a Walkout Basement, and fenced backyard for privacy. Hardwood floors on the main level, and laminated floors on both the Upper level and basement. Three bedrooms, and 3 and half bathrooms. This great community offers an outdoor swimming pool and tot-lot. Close to Kentlands, Crown, and Rio, with all shops and restaurants. Easy access to 1-270, 1-370, and ICC. Less than 3.5 miles to Shady Grove Metro Station. Sellers might need to rent back for a couple of weeks. Open House for December 3, 2023, has been cancelled.
